    "User experienceDiagnostic confidence (with and without AI assistance) was registered as above.",
    "Additionally, the radiologists were asked to provide general feedback on satisfaction, utility, ease of use, and trust on five-point Likert scales, ranging from 'very poor' (score 1) to 'very good' (score 5).",
